(3933, '', 'apricorn-balls', 'Used by trainer in battle\n:   Attempts to catch a wild Pokémon.  If used in a trainer battle, nothing happens and the ball is lost.\n\n    If the wild Pokémon was encountered by fishing, the wild Pokémon\'s catch rate is 3× normal.', NULL, 'lure-ball', 'fc2f40eb-1b7f-4e2d-a078-3b9034747f23.png'),
